title: BRIEF-Lock-up period for Tianjin Zhonghuan Semiconductor's 362.8 mln shares to end

BRIEF-Lock-up period for Tianjin Zhonghuan Semiconductor's 362.8 mln shares to end Sept 14 
Sept 14 Tianjin Zhonghuan Semiconductor Co Ltd 
* Says lock-up period for 362.8 million shares to end, shares to start trading on Sept 16
